Interface PsyTextual

@Type("textual") public interface PsyTextual extends PsyEvaluable, PsyConvertableToInteger, PsyConvertableToIntegral, PsyConvertableToReal, PsyIterable<PsyInteger>, PsyLengthy, PsyScalar<PsyTextual>
The representation of textual, a basic type of mutable and immutable strings.
